narratives.question_text: Were the resources available to you - library, fabrication labs, classroom, software, desk space, etc. adequate for the fulfillment of the assigned work?  If not, please make suggestions.
comments: yes. It was great to use the terrific resources that Yale has.
It was great to have the Beinecke expertise and resources available for the class!
yes. It was great to learn how to do more in-depth research. The Beineche library was a great resource to have.

In most cases, yes. The logistics of getting as-of-yet uncatalogued material at Beinecke scanned for use in our projects -- to say nothing of finding enough time during Beinecke's limited hours for proper research -- presented a challenge, but for the most part, we definitely had access to some pretty cool stuff.
